.\" termin.al-name: theme
.\" termin.al-usage: theme [list|set <name>|system]
.\" termin.al-summary: List, select, or follow the system terminal theme.
.TH THEME 1 "" "termin.al" "termin.al Manual"
.ftr B R
.ftr I R
.ftr BI R
.SH NAME
theme \- List, select, or follow the system terminal theme.
.SH SYNOPSIS
.nf
theme [list|set <name>|system]
.fi
.SH DESCRIPTION
Displays or changes the terminal colour theme. Explicit selections persist in browser storage; system mode follows the active operating-system preference and clears the stored selection.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
.B list
List available theme names.
.TP
.B set name
Select one named theme.
.TP
.B system
Follow the operating-system colour preference.
.SH EXAMPLES
.nf
$ theme list
$ theme set gruber-darker
$ theme system
.fi
.SH SEE ALSO
help(1), man(1)
